  "items": [
    {
      "id": "48bab0719848b1368e156c7431a916018467792432a336535b378a662786e314",
      "text": "If you installed the License Server using the RenderMan Installer then you already have the pixar.license file you need in"
    },
    {
      "id": "933115812c5c44247c1d19b40a811317cbfcb185659bd97f31a5f406c2f1d5ad",
      "text": "C:\\Program Files\\Pixar\\pixar.license"
    },
    {
      "id": "bf06f28dfebc22e9b90a9169121df3fed3ca1449e65eeb16db72cda9c048465f",
      "text": "If you installed by downloading and running the .msi installer then after the installation run the Pixar LicenseApp, which is normally located here:"
    },
    {
      "id": "c895200f3a9287bf65e501dd9363d2ff57d8d69bee4622552b73a6e74acdd15a",
      "text": "C:\\Program Files\\Pixar\\PixarLicense-LA-23.0\\LicenseApp\\bin\\LicenseApp.exe"
    },
    {
      "id": "b3ffd606ec5e0040f0d7bb0c406119fa0ae61ad59d7bac08db647761e567eefa",
      "text": "This will help you download and install the license file for the license server. When LicenseApp discovers there is no license file it will look like:"
    },
    {
      "id": "d873eaf37107fea66a42671a8821bf3377a6a83dac983842ce3ef80ab0de2018",
      "text": "Click the \"Get License\" button to download a new license file for the license server. It will place this license file in:"
    },
    {
      "id": "933115812c5c44247c1d19b40a811317cbfcb185659bd97f31a5f406c2f1d5ad",
      "text": "C:\\Program Files\\Pixar\\pixar.license"
    },
    {
      "id": "193cb16561435c04ce719fc23fe6bbf46d66fc45e19d0b4172eb18e33e489ce2",
      "text": "Note that the default port used by the license server on Windows is 9010. Your administrator should be sure this port is not blocked/firewalled."
    },
    {
      "id": "7bc8a86072b2a7f7faef421d04a08eabc2e66fd93eee217e79384b2dcdf8e41d",
      "text": "If you do have a license, but the license server has not yet been started, RenderMan will report a license error:"
    },
    {
      "id": "2c29e55b009d83a1762e3ac7920a8f9d3827a4d31ccdb3acfeebf6ce9b94c6c5",
      "text": "If you then run the LicenseApp, it will likewise report that it was not able to run contact the license server."
    },
    {
      "id": "c086711e4ea615458ccb9dfe6638443c14d9060094427358ed7e02f770123908",
      "text": "The LicenseApp is a useful tool for indicating the current state of your license server, it can be run on the client machines as well and will remotely query the server for the status."
    },
    {
      "id": "2e32f7efe5c9c9b020d4fdd985686801d22557e9fd19a086b12a368148be07ef",
      "text": "When installing on Windows, the service is automatically installed and started by the installer."
    },
    {
      "id": "484c62f05420ab55b77009559c78c14652456ce99a66c806044de1df59326c63",
      "text": "Starting and Stopping the License Server"
    },
    {
      "id": "a489b49c557c0644665b44fca59e2e01fe0ca2d61fe711c6e62343966998c9db",
      "text": "To start the license service, open the"
    },
    {
      "id": "03029b03191d4ae3afe0bcce277539a3e6e548baa47f40b3ebb8bd53ad07f1ba",
      "text": "Start Menu"
    },
    {
      "id": "94f256ab9891dbcdcbfbf58674c4d804e0650c1b00c30a7ef5526b5a3718ecf4",
      "text": ", type"
    },
    {
      "id": "604dce445e326d952308addc99bd3d0e3ffb0ed9a455e4aa0190641fc5facccc",
      "text": "Services"
    },
    {
      "id": "5a0e0272a4f4e755b1540150fcc3be7bf513ae0a701a86cf2456c3ad7a892fa6",
      "text": "and select the control panel for"
    },
    {
      "id": "604dce445e326d952308addc99bd3d0e3ffb0ed9a455e4aa0190641fc5facccc",
      "text": "Services"
    },
    {
      "id": "e7ac0786668e0ff0f02b62bd04f45ff636fd82db63b1104601c975dc005f3a67",
      "text": ":"
    },
    {
      "id": "b344d80e24a3679999fa964450b34bc24d1578a35509f934c1418b0a20d21a67",
      "text": "The"
    },
    {
      "id": "604dce445e326d952308addc99bd3d0e3ffb0ed9a455e4aa0190641fc5facccc",
      "text": "Services"
    },
    {
      "id": "b662adb67c1e87f561b899e3981e1494e43e572e6b08c37d84b25a363803f43c",
      "text": "control panel will show all the services on Windows, find the one for the Pixar License Server 23.0:"
    },
    {
      "id": "e849068e7b6ae18544d925ee57db7aa85828104a32ecc79257a1e2027be2fe96",
      "text": "From this window you can start, stop, pause and restart the license service."
    },
    {
      "id": "493a670fd3bab8f2279b9a9be4ff59f20337a11f07896a3b4a1ca7316808c7d3",
      "text": "When the License Server is running correctly, the LicenseApp program will display information about license features and the counts:"
    },
    {
      "id": "72c4819829db23cffa0dfa7a6e22e9f6637b195887ce6d074d6e968d5cf38f42",
      "text": "RenderMan and other plugins should then run as expected."
    },
    {
      "id": "13026e0d47a9321a998a4ef7f7a636958f17ca4699fdb6798ea0954ae5bf3b7a",
      "text": "The license server is installed, by default, in C:\\Program Files\\Pixar\\PixarLicense-LA-<version> and contains the following components and scripts:"
    },
    {
      "id": "120f02a648a954ad6ad897351ea94b1d8771ee65a6de77e7c8b90c0857b207aa",
      "text": "PixarLicenseServer"
    },
    {
      "id": "d8655492e55bae62ae16f88aa44f34f1efa4d5a3ae93a0ef900a5a5aba65335c",
      "text": "- the license server program"
    },
    {
      "id": "894f9a4ee6b5972626a7147cbea834a13d29248eabc0b54f5eb74ad7e05cfcfb",
      "text": "LicenseApp\\bin\\LicenseApp.exe"
    },
    {
      "id": "0ec3e554990ead9c2484e7b29095c5b9f1973b18a2c0a188bc4a150f9378c18a",
      "text": "- the license status application"
    },
    {
      "id": "a5932cfdcee91db86304e0d31e50b4e230af5c2b670f3933163060e24c5dd789",
      "text": "queryPRMan.py -"
    },
    {
      "id": "79daf2a8ac5836bdf7e7425799e6f47c6faef39a96a8245ad07dee8674518853",
      "text": "an example python script for querying the license server"
    }
  ]
}